Name: Delicious Stuffed N' Mashed Potatoes
Desc: An exquisitely colorful dish. The eye-catching colors and soft, delicate texture contain overlapping tastes that bump against your tastebuds in a flavor firework show. Such a perfect appetizer leaves you in unsurpassed anticipation for the main dish.
Effect: Restores 30% of Max HP to the selected character and regenerates 790 HP every 5s for 30s.
